reviews.text: Loves this hotel.  Everything is just perfect. Plus my room had a very good view.  And their service is also very good.  I will be back later
10/10 perfect stay. World-class buffet breakfast, excellent front desk, gym and housekeeping. Would stay again.

Hardworking staff.
Service level acceptable.
Price levels align with service levels. Still a lot more to be desired if you are a top~notch big spender.
Hyatt provided excellent service and was very thorough with travel planning for me. The staff was very courteous and ensured all requests that were made were fulfilled to the best of their abilities.

This hotel is in a beautiful location and convenient to the convention center.  I enjoyed the views of the harbor and the large rooms. The food isn't bad, but there are so many restaurants nearby, I barely ate room service.

result.name: 香港君悅酒店

reviews.text:
7/23日在酒店1/F的洗手間，手機忘拿，5分鐘回來找，廁格裡面的人說沒有看到@這時剛好有酒店的保安經過這裡，了解情況後他機智的對我說：不要緊，一會裡面的人出來要是真的沒有，我們會調CCTV，然後報警處理。還不到20秒，裡面傳來聲音，這個手機是你的嗎？
我由衷的感嘆，這裡的保安真的很讚！住這裡很安全👍
也非常感謝那個保安人員，他很客氣的說，這是小事！
